dynGuiComponents.text: Send to c:geo is a browser extension for your PC. When browsing geocaching.com, you can send caches to your smartphone with the click of a button directly inside the browser.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Enables you to open a contact card (of your address book) directly from a log entry, so you can more easily ask friends for help.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: BRouter provides offline routing. If it is installed and has the necessary files downloaded, c:geo will automatically show a route to the cache on the internal map.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Allows easy creation and download of Pocket Queries centred on your current position or a point selected from a map. Requires a Premium Geocaching.com account.
